import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import "./Statistics.css"; const Statistics = () => { const [statistics, setStatistics] = useState({ totalChildren: 0, maleChildren: 0, femaleChildren: 0, vaccinatedChildren: { after_birth: 0, first_month: 0, second_month: 0, fourth_month: 0, month_six: 0, Twelfth_month: 0, Eighteenth_month: 0, }, }); useEffect(() => { fetch("http://localhost:4800/api/doctor/statistics") .then((response) => response.json()) .then((data) => setStatistics(data)) .catch((error) => console.error("Error fetching statistics:", error)); }, []); return (

); }; export default Statistics;
